description:
Aura Kiyoko is a Special Class http://anidb.net/t7112 [Ghoul Investigator], and noteworthy for being the first woman to achieve that rank. She is assigned to the 1st Ward as the Chief of Division I. She is considered to be the model female investigator and is idolized by many women in the organization.
Source: Tokyo Ghoul Wiki
name: Aura Kiyoko
